channel.title: Need a GOOD and WORKING 724 rsps source, client, cache!
channel.description:
hello, moparscapers.
i am looking for a [b]GOOD[/b] and [b]WORKING[/b] rsps [b]source, client, cache[/b] ect... [b]i prefer a 724 rsps.[/b](something like matrix) i have looked on every possible site for a good and working rsps for myself but everytime no good results. and lots of people said that moparscape is a good site for help so i listenend to those people and hoping for good results. so i hope 1 of you guys have a good rsps for me so i can code it myself to what i like.
[b]preference:[/b]
-non or just a few bugs -new armour style's with working aura's (not necessarily but its just nice :D) -not much work on it (not that i'm lazy but just to save some time) -working skills -eco or spawn i dont really care
i hope you guys can help me with this soon
regards,tlol
btw w00t my first post :D
(sorry that my english sucks i'm not so good at it but i try to do my best! :P)
